oticeable impact on the interpretation of\npresent limits from Fermi-LAT and WMAP+ACT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2012 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2012 17:19:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 10 Aug 2012 02:38:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-13"}
