 the longitudinal oscillations\nand the later eruption of a prominence thread, as well as a coronal mass\nejection (CME), is also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Apr 2012 13:18:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
