though various\ndistinct ordered states detected below T* are not yet understood. I also\nunderline the large contrast between the scientific behaviours which prevailed\nbetween these two periods of scientific activity. I suggest that these changes\nmight have a negative incidence, in my opinion, on the research and education\nsystem, at least in our field of science.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Apr 2012 14:44:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-04-18"}
